OL,7,FHe was found guilty at Manchester
OL,8,FCrown Court of committing 12 offences
OL,9,Fagainst 10 women and girls, the
OL,10,Fyoungest of whom was 13 years old.
OL,12,FThe court heard that Emmerson's
OL,13,Fvictims recalled how he smiled while
OL,14,Fhe attacked them in a 'bear hug',
OL,15,Fbefore pinning them to the ground and
OL,16,Fgroping them.
OL,18,FAll the victims were able to escape
OL,19,Fhis grasp and report the incidents to
OL,20,Fthe police.
