OL,7,FThe "depraved" attacker was identified
OL,8,Fas a suspect after officers noticed a
OL,9,F'pattern' of offences between November
OL,10,F2023 and April 2024.
OL,12,FEmmerson, from Lancaster Court in
OL,13,FManchester, was eventually tracked
OL,14,Fdown by Greater Manchester Police
OL,15,Fafter the two alleged assaults on 15
OL,16,FApril 2024.
OL,18,FThey were able to use CCTV to trace
OL,19,Fhis movements, and he was arrested
OL,20,Fdays later at his ex-partner's house
OL,21,Fin Wythenshawe, Manchester.
